| `system/fvSolution` | Increase `nSweeps` from 5 to 10 for all solvers (`rho`, `rhoU`, `rhoE`, `U`, `e`) — this provides more relaxation iterations when the solution develops sharp gradients near the step, making the iterative solve more robust. |

